## What is the AI Dev Gallery?

![bg right:35% contain](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/microsoft/ai-dev-gallery/main/docs/images/HeroImage1.png)

- **Open-source** Windows app from Microsoft
- Available free in the **Microsoft Store**
- Integrate **AI capabilities** into your native Windows apps
- Discover AI scenarios & models
- Built with **WinUI** & **Windows App SDK**

---

## Key Features

<div class="columns">
<div>

### 🧠 Models & Samples

- **25+ interactive samples** powered by local AI models
- Browse and download models from **Hugging Face** and **GitHub**
- Supports **Phi Silica** on Copilot+ PCs

</div>
<div>

### 🛠️ Developer Experience

- View **C# source code** for every sample
- **Export standalone Visual Studio projects** with a single click
- Works **offline** — models run locally
- Supports **x64** and **ARM64**

</div>
</div>

